These are Puzzles for 3x4 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-1::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: cola, fanta, mirinda, sprite
The people have 4 different jobs:  project-manager, social-worker, freelancer, paramedic
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: country, electronic, dubstep, classical
1. the fan of classical is on the right of the fan of electronic##1
2. the person drinking mirinda is on the left of the person drinking cola##1
3. the person drinking sprite is on the left of the freelancer##1
4. the person drinking cola is the project-manager##1
5. the project-manager is on the right of the freelancer##1
6. the fan of country is on the left of the paramedic##1
7. the social-worker is on the left of the fan of dubstep##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |   2    |     3      |     4      |
| Beverage    | fanta  | sprite | mirinda    | cola       |
| Job         | social-worker | paramedic    | freelancer      | project-manager |
| Music-Genre   | country   | dubstep | electronic | classical        |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-2::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: ivory, brown, pink, ebony
The people have 4 different jobs:  fisherman, lawyer, musician, social-worker
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: alhambra, prince, chaman, bongani
1. the bongani-smoker is on the left of the social-worker##1
2. the person who likes ebony is on the right of the chaman-smoker##1
3. the musician is on the right of the person who likes pink##1
4. the prince-smoker is on the left of the bongani-smoker##1
5. the alhambra-smoker is the fisherman##1
6. the bongani-smoker is the person who likes brown##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |    2     |       3       |     4     |
| Color        | pink   | brown | ivory     | ebony      |
| Job         | lawyer | musician | social-worker | fisherman |
| Cigar   | prince    | bongani   | chaman     | alhambra      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-3::.
4 different pets are kept: snake, guinea-pig, cat, mouse
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: country, electronic, hip-hop, pop
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: sailing, skateboarding, basketball, swimming
1. the fan of electronic is on the right of the owner of the snake##1
2. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the right of the owner of the cat##1
3. the fan of pop is on the far left##1
4. the owner of the mouse is the fan of hip-hop##1
5. the person who's sport is swimming is on the right of the fan of electronic##1
6. the person who's sport is swimming is on the right of the person who's sport is basketball##1
7. the owner of the snake is the person who's sport is sailing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |       2       |    3    |      4      |
| Pet         | snake | guinea-pig | cat | mouse |
| Music-Genre   | pop       | electronic    | country | hip-hop     |
| Sport   | sailing | basketball    | swimming | skateboarding    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-4::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  architect, firefighter, freelancer, project-manager
There are 4 different favourite colors: emerald, aquamarine, grey, black
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: march, july, february, december
1. the freelancer is the person who's birthday is in december##1
2. the person who likes aquamarine is on the far left##1
3. the person who's birthday is in february is on the right of the person who's birthday is in december##1
4. the firefighter is on the far right##1
5. the person who likes grey is on the far right##1
6. the person who likes emerald is the freelancer##1
7. the freelancer is on the left of the person who likes grey##1
8. the project-manager is on the right of the person who's birthday is in july##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |        2        |     3      |      4      |
| Job         | architect | project-manager | freelancer | firefighter |
| Color       | aquamarine     | black      | emerald     | grey      |
| Birthday   | july | march         | december      | february        |

