.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-5::.
There 4 different types of food: lemon, peas, cranberry, cabbage
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: trance, d&b, indie, salsa
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: badminton, biathlon, climbing, snowboarding
1. the fan of d&b is on the far right##1
2. the person eating cranberry is on the far left##1
3. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the right of the fan of trance##1
4. the person who's sport is badminton is the fan of indie##1
5. the person eating lemon is on the right of the person who's sport is biathlon##1
6. the person eating lemon is the fan of d&b##1
7. the person eating cabbage is the person who's sport is climbing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |    3     |      4       |
| Food         | cranberry   | cabbage | peas  | lemon      |
| Music-Genre   | indie  | trance        | salsa  | d&b       |
| Sport         | badminton | climbing    | biathlon | snowboarding |

