.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-6::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  accountant, designer, mechanic, writer
The people have 4 different hobbies: traveling, photography, chess, baking
The people use 4 different means of transport: bus, scooter, car, taxi
1. the accountant is the person driving the scooter##1
2. the person driving the bus is on the right of the person driving the taxi##1
3. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the right of the writer##1
4. the person driving the taxi is on the far left##1
5. the designer is on the far left##1
6. the person who's hobby is chess is the mechanic##1
7. the person driving the scooter is on the right of the person who's hobby is photography##1
8. the writer is the person driving the car##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |   3    |     4      |
| Job           | designer | mechanic | writer | accountant |
| Hobby   | baking   | chess  | photography | traveling   |
| Transport   | taxi   | bus     | car | scooter       |

