.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-7::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: march, august, july, may
The people have 4 different hobbies: baking, cooking, skydiving, video-games
There are 4 different favourite colors: aquamarine, red, ebony, azure
1. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the far right##1
2. the person who's birthday is in august is on the far right##1
3. the person who likes aquamarine is on the left of the person who likes red##1
4. the person who likes red is the person who's birthday is in july##1
5. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the right of the person who's birthday is in march##1
6. the person who likes ebony is on the left of the person who likes aquamarine##1
7. the person who's hobby is baking is on the right of the person who's hobby is cooking##1
8. the person who's hobby is cooking is the person who likes aquamarine##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |    3    |     4     |
| Birthday          | march  | may | july   | august     |
| Hobby         | video-games | cooking   | baking  | skydiving |
| Color   | ebony         | aquamarine  | red | azure  |

