.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-8::.
City: rome, miami, san-francisco, colone
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: animation, crime, drama, mystery
There are 4 different favourite colors: grey, chestnut, green, blue
1. the person traveling to miami is the person who likes green##1
2. the person who likes blue is on the right of the person watching mystery movies##1
3. the person watching crime movies is on the far right##1
4. the person watching drama movies is on the left of the person who likes green##1
5. the person traveling to colone is on the left of the person watching animation movies##1
6. the person who likes blue is the person traveling to san-francisco##1
7. the person who likes chestnut is on the left of the person who likes blue##1
8. the person traveling to miami is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |      3      |    4     |
| City      | colone | san-francisco     | rome | miami |
| Movie-Genre   | mystery  | animation | drama       | crime    |
| Color   | chestnut   | blue | grey    | green |

