.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-9::.
There 4 different types of food: cucumber, onion, pepper, tomato
The people use 4 different means of transport: van, roller, jet-ski, trike
House: ranch-style, gothic-revival, cape-cod, townhouse
1. the person driving the roller is on the right of the person eating tomato##1
2. the townhouse house is on the right of the cape-cod house##1
3. the person driving the roller is on the left of the person driving the jet-ski##1
4. the cape-cod house is the person eating onion##1
5. the person eating onion is on the right of the person driving the trike##1
6. the person driving the trike is on the right of the person eating pepper##1
7. the gothic-revival house is on the left of the ranch-style house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2     |   3    |     4      |
| Food          | pepper        | tomato   | onion  | cucumber   |
| Transport   | van         | trike     | roller    | jet-ski       |
| House         | gothic-revival | ranch-style | cape-cod | townhouse |

