.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-10::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: game, baccarat, tiparillo, aristoff
There 4 different types of food: pumpkin, spinach, tomato, zucchini
There are 4 different favourite colors: light-blue, mauve, ivory, chestnut
1. the aristoff-smoker is the person who likes chestnut##1
2. the person who likes mauve is on the left of the person who likes ivory##1
3. the tiparillo-smoker is on the left of the person eating spinach##1
4. the game-smoker is on the right of the person who likes chestnut##1
5. the person eating tomato is on the far right##1
6. the tiparillo-smoker is on the left of the person who likes chestnut##1
7. the person eating pumpkin is on the right of the baccarat-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Cigar   | baccarat    | tiparillo | aristoff | game        |
| Food       | zucchini | pumpkin  | spinach | tomato     |
| Color        | mauve    | ivory   | chestnut  | light-blue |

