.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-11::.
There 4 different types of food: blueberry, spinach, onion, eggplant
4 different games are played: bridge, mah-jongg, canasta, backgammon
The people use 4 different means of transport: airplane, car, scooter, tram
1. the person driving the airplane is on the far left##1
2. the person playing bridge is on the right of the person eating spinach##1
3. the person playing mah-jongg is on the left of the person playing backgammon##1
4. the person playing bridge is on the right of the person playing backgammon##1
5. the person driving the tram is on the right of the person driving the car##1
6. the person driving the airplane is on the left of the person eating eggplant##1
7. the person playing bridge is the person driving the scooter##1
8. the person playing canasta is the person eating blueberry##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |      2       |       3       |       4       |
| Food         | blueberry  | eggplant | spinach  | onion |
| Game       | canasta | mah-jongg        | backgammon | bridge       |
| Transport   | airplane   | car          | tram          | scooter       |

