.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-12::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: milk, water, tea, iced-tea
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: adventure, disaster, documentary, mystery
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: volleyball, swimming, basketball, biathlon
1. the person drinking milk is on the right of the person watching adventure movies##1
2. the person watching mystery movies is the person drinking water##1
3. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the left of the person who's sport is volleyball##1
4. the person watching mystery movies is on the right of the person watching disaster movies##1
5. the person drinking tea is on the right of the person drinking iced-tea##1
6. the person drinking milk is the person who's sport is basketball##1
7. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |     3      |    4    |
| Beverage         | iced-tea   | tea   | milk | water |
| Movie-Genre   | documentary | adventure | disaster   | mystery |
| Sport   | biathlon     | volleyball  | basketball  | swimming  |

