.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-13::.
House: palace, modern, townhouse, wooden
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: blues, metal, rock, trance
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: february, july, march, january
1. the modern house is on the left of the fan of trance##1
2. the person who's birthday is in march is the fan of trance##1
3. the townhouse house is on the right of the person who's birthday is in march##1
4. the person who's birthday is in march is on the left of the person who's birthday is in january##1
5. the person who's birthday is in february is on the right of the fan of metal##1
6. the person who's birthday is in march is on the left of the fan of blues##1
7. the person who's birthday is in february is on the left of the palace house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |       3       |    4    |
| House         | wooden | modern    | palace        | townhouse |
| Music-Genre   | metal     | rock     | trance        | blues   |
| Birthday         | july   | february | march | january  |

