.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-14::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: siglo, davidoff, fonseca, oliveros
There are 4 different nationalities: canadian, indonesian, pakistani, russian
There are 4 different favourite beverages: water, 7up, iced-tea, lemonade
1. the siglo-smoker is on the right of the pakistani##1
2. the person drinking 7up is on the right of the russian##1
3. the canadian is on the left of the person drinking water##1
4. the person drinking lemonade is on the left of the pakistani##1
5. the siglo-smoker is on the right of the person drinking 7up##1
6. the oliveros-smoker is on the left of the siglo-smoker##1
7. the fonseca-smoker is on the far right##1
8. the indonesian is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |     3     |     4      |
| Cigar   | davidoff   | oliveros  | siglo    | fonseca    |
| Nationality   | russian | pakistani  | canadian  | indonesian |
| Beverage     | lemonade  | 7up | iced-tea | water        |

