.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-15::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: coffee, iced-tea, tea, water
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: chaman, aristoff, oliveros, montecristo
4 different pets are kept: bird, ferret, hamster, rat
1. the owner of the bird is the person drinking tea##1
2. the person drinking tea is on the right of the aristoff-smoker##1
3. the aristoff-smoker is on the right of the montecristo-smoker##1
4. the owner of the ferret is on the right of the owner of the rat##1
5. the montecristo-smoker is the person drinking water##1
6. the oliveros-smoker is on the right of the owner of the hamster##1
7. the person drinking coffee is the chaman-smoker##1
8. the oliveros-smoker is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2     |    3     |    4     |
| Beverage      | coffee        | water    | iced-tea | tea      |
| Cigar   | chaman        | montecristo   | aristoff  | oliveros  |
| Pet         | rat | ferret | hamster   | bird |

