.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-16::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: taxi, ship, bus, motorbike
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: biathlon, handball, lacrosse, snowboarding
4 different pets are kept: bird, fish, horse, rabbit
1. the person driving the motorbike is on the right of the person driving the taxi##1
2. the owner of the rabbit is on the left of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
3. the owner of the bird is on the right of the owner of the fish##1
4. the person driving the ship is the owner of the horse##1
5. the person driving the motorbike is on the left of the person driving the bus##1
6. the person who's sport is lacrosse is the person driving the bus##1
7. the person driving the bus is on the left of the person who's sport is handball##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |     3     |     4     |
| Transport          | taxi     | motorbike   | bus | ship |
| Sport   | biathlon | snowboarding | lacrosse | handball   |
| Pet           | rabbit    | fish     | bird      | horse     |

