.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-20::.
House: gothic-revival, victorian, craftsman, tower
There are 4 different favourite beverages: lemonade, water, 7up, iced-tea
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: badminton, biathlon, parkour, tennis
1. the victorian house is on the left of the person drinking lemonade##1
2. the person who's sport is badminton is on the left of the craftsman house##1
3. the person who's sport is tennis is on the far right##1
4. the person drinking 7up is on the far right##1
5. the person drinking lemonade is the person who's sport is parkour##1
6. the person drinking iced-tea is on the far left##1
7. the tower house is on the far right##1
8. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left of the person who's sport is parkour##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |     3      |       4        |
| House           | victorian  | craftsman  | gothic-revival | tower |
| Beverage   | iced-tea   | lemonade | water   | 7up      |
| Sport         | badminton | parkour    | biathlon   | tennis         |

 